  compressible Navier Stokes (Godunov)
  one step
  exit
  turn off twilight
  recompute dt interval
    2
  turn off twilight
  final time $tFinal
  times to plot $tPlot
*
*
  plot and always wait
*
  show file options
    compressed
     open
      $show
